parameters:
Crawling through the forest, with the sound of
battle echoing, I manage to reach my destination
despite my injured body.
I collapse, covered in blood, next to the woman.

The man was stunned when he saw the woman. She was
breathing weakly, but it didn't seem like it would
last long.

The amount of blood flowing is too much. The wound
is also too large to be closed.

The man couldn't respond to the woman's words. He
knew that he couldn't do anything to help her. In
fact, he had no means to save her.

\nw[Female Elf]Ugh... Too strong...! Both of you, run away
quickly!

Nearby, a female elf is fighting to protect the
men who have collapsed from the giants.

However, it can't be called a battle. The female
elf's attacks have no effect on the giants, and
she is solely focused on evading as a decoy.
\nw[Man]This wound... it's not enough... for this guy...

\nw[Female Elf]If that's the case, then run away even if you're
alone!

Suddenly, it seemed as if the movements of the
female elf had slowed down in response to the
giant's roar. And at that moment...

The giant's attack couldn't be completely avoided
and hit the leg. The giant then launched another
attack at the immobilized female elf, causing her
body to be blown away like a ball and roll near
the man.

The giant seemed to lose interest in us and ran
off to another location. There must be other prey
it wants to hunt.
However, such things didn't matter to the man.

The lower half of the female elf's body was
crushed like paper. It seems that when she hit the
ground, her head also hit, and blood is flowing
from her head.
She didn't even flinch... she didn't move at all.

The man's scream echoed through the forest, where
the battle was still raging.

\nw[???]Are you okay? You were having a really intense
nightmare.
\nw[???]Are you okay? Can you tell me your name?
Is it alright if I call you \N[21]?
\nw[\N[21]]I am \N[21]. I work as a mercenary.
Is it alright if I call you \N[1]?
\nw[\N[21]]You're \N[1], right? My childhood friend and lover.

\nw[\N[1]]You seem fine. We're about to go in, but do you
understand the situation?

\nw[\N[21]]Ah, it's a bandit extermination. I understand. I
took a nap to rest until it's time for a surprise
attack.

\nw[\N[1]]What's wrong? Are you spacing out again? Are you
still half asleep?
Is it alright if I call you \N[3]?

\nw[\N[3]]Is that so? Even though it's been a while since
we've worked together, don't let your guard down.

\nw[\N[3]]We should have time until the guard change, but
unexpected situations can happen, so let's hurry.
\nw[\N[21]]I understand. It's a bandit capture, right.

You can change the movement speed in the menu
options.
